snippet.title: Quake: Blue Monday Jam - Icemecha Dojo Co-op
snippet.description:
Running through the Blue Monday Jam on co-op with QSS. Definitely a fun mapset for the handful of maps we made it through. Here is Icemecha Dojo. We forgot to run back out to do the silver key area. For some reason I didn't think the exit was going to be the exit.

February 2, 2021
